James Noble (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Noble_(actor) 0 James Wilkes Noble (March 5, 1922 – March 28, 2016) was an American actor, best known for his portrayal of sweet-natured, naive Governor Eugene X. Gatling on ABC's 1979–86 sitcom Benson.
